Binary Search Tree (BST)

This project contains a complete implementation of Binary Search Tree (BST) in Java with multiple operations and algorithms for academic learning and Data Structures practice.

Features Implemented

- BST Insertion
- Tree Traversals
  - Inorder
  - Preorder
  - Postorder
  - Level Order
- Minimum Element Search
- Node Count and Sum of Nodes
- Average of Tree Values
- Height of Tree
- Count of Leaf Nodes
- Range Printing (X to Y)
- Print All Root-to-Leaf Paths
- Delete Node in BST
- Valid BST Check
- Lowest Common Ancestor (LCA)


